UrbanWiki shirts are made to fit males our shirts are made with high-quality, 100% spun polyester and deliver the look and feel of organic cotton with the wickability of poly-performance fibers, providing a great fit with a soft feel.UrbanWiki shirts however provide the body with a great fit and the high fashion appeal. Our shirts are not double sided prints and are all hand made in the USA with fabrics which have been treated with sublimation printing.   

 


Shipping worldwide: 
2-3 days shipping received. 
Tracking provided when order is shipped

Please note:
 *Pre orders are always shipped first when the product becomes available.
 *All international customer orders will be billed the shipping cost.
